"Une description complète de ce sujet peut être consultée dans la section "
"<link linkend=\"details.impexp.qifimp\">Importation QIF</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to importing QIF format files, &kmymoney; can directly open data "
"files used by <link linkend=\"details.impexp.gnucash\">&gnucash;</link> file."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
